        <abstract> 
<p>Thanks HS for the preface to the 3d edition [of <hi rend="italic">Die Thierzucht</hi> (1872)].</p>  
<p>Has purchased H. von Nathusius’ work [? <hi rend="italic">Vorträge über Viehzucht und Rassenkenntniss</hi>, Th. 1 (1872)]; feels he has ignored all that CD has attempted to make out with respect to domesticated animals.</p> 
